Mame-Anna Diop (amụrụ n'ọnwa Febụwarị 6, 1988) bụ onye America na-eme ihe nkiri na ihe nlereanya. Kemgbe afọ 2018, ọ gosipụtara Kory Anders na DC Universe / HBO Max usoro Titans
Diop bụkwa usoro na-aga n'ihu na CW supernatural mystery The Messengers (2015) na Fox thriller 24: Legacy (2017)
Na ihe nkiri, ọ pụtara na Us (2019) ma bụrụ onye isi Nanny (2022).

A mụrụ Diop na Senegal ma ọ kwaga United States mgbe ọ dị afọ isii. Ọ kwagara mba New York mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na isii iji chụsoo ọrụ na ime ihe nkiri na ime ihe ngosi. N'afọ 2006, o mere ihe nkiri telivishọn mbụ ya na ọrụ ugboro ugboro na Everybody Hates Chris
N'ime afọ ndị sochirinụ, ọ bụ onye ọbịa na Lincoln Heights, Whitney, na Touch

Diop nwere ọrụ na ihe nkiri afọ 2013 The Moment N'afọ 2015, Diop pụtara dịka Rose Arvale na usoro ihe nkiri karịrị nke mmadụ nke dị mkpirikpi The Messengers Ka e mesịrị n'afọ ahụ, ọ pụtara na usoro ihe nkiri Quantico ma tinye ya na ọrụ ugboro ugboro na usoro ihe omume Oprah Greenleaf N'afọ 2017, Diop bụ usoro na-aga n'ihu na usoro 24: Legacy N'ime usoro DC Universe superhero Titans (afọ 2018), Diop na-eme nwa eze na onye dike Starfire. N'afọ 2018, a tụbara Diop na ihe nkiri egwu Us nke Jordan Peele duziri.
